### default policy ###

config defaults
        option syn_flood        1
        option input            ACCEPT
        option output           ACCEPT
        option forward          ACCEPT
        option disable_ipv6     1

### VLANs policy ###

config zone
        option name             LAN_ONO
        list   network          'LAN_ONO'
        option input            ACCEPT
        option output           ACCEPT
        option forward          ACCEPT

config zone
        option name             LAN_MV
        list   network          'LAN_MV'
        option input            ACCEPT
        option output           ACCEPT
        option forward          ACCEPT

config zone
        option name             WAN_DMZ
        list   network          'WAN_DMZ'
        option input            ACCEPT
        option output           ACCEPT
        option forward          ACCEPT
        option masq             1
        option mtu_fix          1

### VLANs forwarding ###

config forwarding
        option src              LAN_ONO
        option dest             WAN_DMZ
        option mtu_fix          1
